@Test public void testRightOuterStrategy1() {     this.testRightOuterStrategies(JoinHint.OPTIMIZER_CHOOSES). }

private void testRightOuterStrategies(JoinHint hint) {     final ExecutionEnvironment env = ExecutionEnvironment.getExecutionEnvironment().     DataSet<Tuple5<Integer, Long, String, Long, Integer>> ds1 = env.fromCollection(emptyTupleData, tupleTypeInfo).     DataSet<Tuple5<Integer, Long, String, Long, Integer>> ds2 = env.fromCollection(emptyTupleData, tupleTypeInfo).     // should work     ds1.rightOuterJoin(ds2, hint).where(0).equalTo(4).with(new DummyJoin()). }
@Override public Long join(Tuple5<Integer, Long, String, Long, Integer> v1, Tuple5<Integer, Long, String, Long, Integer> v2) throws Exception {     return 1L. }
@Override public Integer getKey(Tuple5<Integer, Long, String, Long, Integer> v) throws Exception {     return v.f0. }
@Override public Long getKey(Tuple5<Integer, Long, String, Long, Integer> v) throws Exception {     return v.f1. }
